{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-db8eed2b-7c20-40fc-8cce-e375b03502ae-106\nfc_5da460a3-57c6-996e-a38e-4e0403431304_3","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI/studio-v2/02-角色库与人设编辑.md","offset":45,"limit":30},"result":{"success":{"content":"|------|------|\n| 角色库详情页 | `CharacterDetailEditForm` + BASIC/PROMPT items；保存走 API |\n| 故事编辑器选中锚点 | `StoryEditorCharacterModals` 复用同一套 items；打开前 `fetchCharacterDef` |\n| 画布「添加角色」 | 先走精简 `CREATE_CHARACTER_*` → `commitCreateCharacter`，再可编辑详情槽 |\n\n画布角色锚点 **打开时**由 `bundle.participants` + `/api/characters` 的 displayName 生成（`diskBundleGraph`）；`pendingCardCount` 由当前包内卡归属统计。**不是**独立 mock 数组；完整人设仍按 agentId 从 API 取。\n\n## 4. persona.personalityCode 业务理解\n\n- Studio：Select 写入投影字段；保存时 trim 后进 CharacterDef。  \n- 引擎：见 [05-引擎Composer与personalityCode.md](./05-引擎Composer与personalityCode.md)。  \n- UI helperText 已写明会进 Composer systemHard（演示口径；Host 真跑另议）。\n\n## 5. 已知小不一致（勿当 bug 乱修扩大范围）\n\n- 部分磁盘 `voiceId`（如 `zh_child_boy`、`zh_male_elder`）**不在** `REALTIME_VOICE_OPTIONS` 枚举内；下拉可能显示空/异常，属音色枚举未扩全，与 MBTI 任务无关。  \n- `createEmptyCharacterDetailSlots` 默认 personalityCode = 选项表第一项（ISTJ），新建后再改。\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":62,"fileSize":3445,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI/studio-v2/02-角色库与人设编辑.md","readRange":{"startLine":45,"endLine":62},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-db8eed2b-7c20-40fc-8cce-e375b03502ae-106\nfc_5da460a3-57c6-996e-a38e-4e0403431304_3","startedAtMs":"1784771665346","completedAtMs":"1784771665511"},"model_call_id":"60f67b1d-3ad1-4611-9cc4-6aa32a145540-28-xs6o","session_id":"79bbae55-4798-4921-9584-898a64ef9b19","timestamp_ms":1784771665472}
